  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1000320/" class="title-link">短评：书的八卦</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1000320"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/btr/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1000476-7.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/btr/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">btr</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2005-05-08"
      class="main-meta">2005-05-08 02:27:33</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1000320_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                   每个爱书人都不会错过“关于书的书”。因为关于书的书就是书的八卦。八卦的好，在于令一个命题有了宽泛的触角，且往往以有趣与否作为标准。  古董书、老杂志、可以吃的书、书架、图书馆、传奇书店，还有形形色色的书店和书人，《书天堂》展示的是一个诱人的书的世界，读罢全书...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">5有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1000320_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1000320_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
